{"sha": "6602b2f1c777e6e563a7bcc920bbd1ee1c4f7eab", "node_id": "MDY6Q29tbWl0NzI0NzEyOjY2MDJiMmYxYzc3N2U2ZTU2M2E3YmNjOTIwYmJkMWVlMWM0ZjdlYWI=", "commit": {"author": {"name": "bors", "email": "bors@rust-lang.org", "date": "2015-09-20T18:04:52Z"}, "committer": {"name": "bors", "email": "bors@rust-lang.org", "date": "2015-09-20T18:04:52Z"}, "message": "Auto merge of #28501 - semarie:stdcpp-path, r=alexcrichton\n\nBy default, the linker in use under OpenBSD is the linker of base, which\r\ndon't include /usr/local/lib where libstdc++ of gcc-4.9 lives. We need\r\nto add this directory to linker-path-search (using -L).\r\n\r\nSearch the path of libstdc++.a, which is a known name (libstdc++.so has\r\nSO_VERSION) in the same directory.\r\n\r\nr? @alexcrichton \r\n\r\nthis commit needs #28495 to be commited first. It should be the last piece for building rustc under OpenBSD from scratch.", "tree": {"sha": "4a102c07089b755c16dfc455a016340612e46a3b", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/git/trees/4a102c07089b755c16dfc455a016340612e46a3b"}, "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/git/commits/6602b2f1c777e6e563a7bcc920bbd1ee1c4f7eab", "comment_count": 0, "verification": {"verified": false, "reason": "unsigned", "signature": null, "payload": null}}, "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/commits/6602b2f1c777e6e563a7bcc920bbd1ee1c4f7eab", "html_url": "https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/commit/6602b2f1c777e6e563a7bcc920bbd1ee1c4f7eab", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/commits/6602b2f1c777e6e563a7bcc920bbd1ee1c4f7eab/comments", "author": {"login": "bors", "id": 3372342, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjMzNzIzNDI=", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/3372342?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/bors", "html_url": "https://github.com/bors", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bors/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bors/following{/other_user}", "gists_u